graph TD
    TaskState["TaskState（联合类型）"]
    
    subgraph 7种具体类型
        LST["LocalShellTask\ntype: 'local_bash'\n特有: command"]
        LAT["LocalAgentTask\ntype: 'local_agent'\n特有: agentId, messages"]
        RAT["RemoteAgentTask\ntype: 'remote_agent'\n特有: 远程端点"]
        IPT["InProcessTeammateTask\ntype: 'in_process_teammate'\n特有: 进程内上下文"]
        LWT["LocalWorkflowTask\ntype: 'local_workflow'\n特有: 工作流步骤"]
        MMT["MonitorMcpTask\ntype: 'monitor_mcp'\n特有: MCP服务标识"]
        DT["DreamTask\ntype: 'dream'\n特有: 异步载荷"]
    end

    subgraph TaskStateBase共有字段
        BASE["id / type / status\ndescription / startTime\noutputFile / notified"]
    end
    
    subgraph 5种共享状态
        STATUS["pending → running\n→ completed / failed / killed"]
    end

    TaskState --> LST & LAT & RAT & IPT & LWT & MMT & DT
    LST & LAT & RAT & IPT & LWT & MMT & DT --> BASE
    BASE --> STATUS
